  "3194840": {
    "name": "Spring Tales",
    "steam_appid": 3194840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/0c8fce0847c1b059c206149e5458e39d.poster.avif?t=1769709455\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/0c8fce0847c1b059c206149e5458e39d.webm?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/0c8fce0847c1b059c206149e5458e39d.mp4?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《春之物语》是一款温馨治愈的二维解谜冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解决谜题、克服挑战、重建家园，帮助布洛瑟姆镇的可爱居民筹备春日庆典。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一个充满友情、希望与社区温情的动人故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/ce4865af985f749b4bf168af6faa1622.poster.avif?t=1769709455\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/ce4865af985f749b4bf168af6faa1622.webm?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/ce4865af985f749b4bf168af6faa1622.mp4?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《春之物语》带你走进布洛瑟姆镇——一个温馨的小镇。暴风雨过后，居民们正齐心协力筹备春日庆典，努力让生活重回正轨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将跟随五位性格各异的角色，一起经历修复与筹备的旅程。在帮助他们解开谜题的过程中，也将逐步了解他们背后的故事与心声。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/83e12ff929559c4b2fecea6ecfd6588e.poster.avif?t=1769709455\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/83e12ff929559c4b2fecea6ecfd6588e.webm?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/83e12ff929559c4b2fecea6ecfd6588e.mp4?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《春之物语》包含多种趣味解谜玩法，考验你的分类、堆叠与组合能力。从修理电路，到将物品按顺序整理，每个谜题都富有创意，带来新鲜体验与小小挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不断尝试，你将发现丰富多样的解法与隐藏的细节，享受探索的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/63a3b2b67f14a8cfe063c2bf8675c319.poster.avif?t=1769709455\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/63a3b2b67f14a8cfe063c2bf8675c319.webm?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/63a3b2b67f14a8cfe063c2bf8675c319.mp4?t=1769709455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随五位角色的日常与心路历程，他们在春日庆典中各有自己的角色与故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欣赏手绘风格的画面，感受小镇的细腻与温度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜元素融入剧情，帮助角色一步步完成他们的任务与心愿。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时暂停步伐，沉浸在布洛瑟姆镇宁静治愈的氛围中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证一个社区如何在风暴后重建、疗愈，并一同庆祝春天的到来。</p></li></ul>",
